reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Not the best mounting kit
reviews.reviewText: I bought this to go with my new Freezer 34 eports duo for my intel 12th gen setup. With this hardware kit the CPU cooler did NOT touch the processor. I kept wondering why it would shut down while i was trying to install windows and after i finally got it installed it was super laggy to i downloaded CPUID to check on things and the CPU's temp were at 100c. So yeah this hardware kit isnt the best. Luckily my cooler for my 9700k had brackets that would fit....
